---
title: Pancetta and Chorizo Penne with Roasted Tomatoes and Creamy Red Sauce
description: Double the meat, double the cheese: that’s what you get with this rich, hearty pasta that uses both pancetta and chorizo as well as Parmesan and cream cheese. They’re tossed into a tomato-y sauce, fulfilling all of your pasta-night dreams. You can’t have all that deliciousness without a few veggies, of course, so we’re also adding juicy roasted tomato wedges and sweet peas.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pancetta-and-chorizo-penne-8f26a6d9.jpg
